"path":"api/articles/GuoFeng_CaoFeng.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1658239840558-8f8252792ca1?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80","text":"《国风·曹风》是《诗经》十五国风之一，共四篇。曹，国名。西周初周武王封其弟曹叔振铎(duó)于曹国，建都陶丘(今山东省菏泽市定陶区)。公元前487年为宋景公所灭。曹国的统治区在今山东菏泽地区一带。曹风就是这一区域的诗。曹诗产生的时代，从内容判断，多为东迁以后，在风诗中，它产生的时...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":853,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"国风","slug":"国风","count":15,"path":"api/categories/国风.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"诗经","slug":"诗经","count":15,"path":"api/tags/诗经.json"},{"name":"国风","slug":"国风","count":15,"path":"api/tags/国风.json"}],"author":{"name":"ORLA","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2022/07/05/f30c5a60868494ae.png","link":"/","description":"LIFE AND DREAM","socials":{"github":"https://github.com","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"https://weibo.com","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com","csdn":"https://csdn.net","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}